: 919-924.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn5"></a><a href="#_ftnref5">[5]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">Fyfe, Gillett and Zwiers: </span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">Overestimated global warming over the past 20 years.  </span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt; font-style:italic">Nature Climate Change</span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt"> </span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">3</span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">, 767–769 </span><span style="color:#262626; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">(2013)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 9pt; text-indent:-9pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">von Storch, Barkhordarian, Hasselman, Zorita:  Can climate models explain the recent stagnation in global warming? </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">(2013) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:8pt">http://www.academia.edu/4210419/Can_climate_models_explain_the_recent_stagnation_in_global_warming</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 9pt; text-indent:-9pt"><a name="_ftn6"></a><a href="#_ftnref6">[6]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt">  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman